code:
sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server
    participant database

    webURL https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi

    browser->>server: GET webURL/exampleapp/notes
    activate server
    server-->>browser: HTML document
    deactivate server

    browser->>server: GET webURL/exampleapp/main.js
    activate server
    server-->>browser: Javascript file (main.js)
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: The browser executes javascript code (main.js)

    browser->>server: GET webURL/exampleapp/data.json
    activate server
    server-->>browser: data.json
    deactivate server
    
    Note right of browser: The browser handles data.json and renders new elements based on data that data.json has in it.

    browser->>server: POST webURL/exampleapp/new_note
    activate server
    server-->>database: INSERT INTO notes (note_field) VALUES (note_name)
    server-->>browser: GET webURL/exampleapp/notes
    deactivate server
